product.title: Lambert - The Jade Vegan Leather Backpack in Black
product.body_html: Made with premium, PETA-certified vegan leather, this high-end backpack blends functionality and aesthetics by offering weather-resistant properties, a refined design, a large storage capacity, and numerous interior pockets to keep you going no matter the day, no matter the weather. 40cm (height) x 30cm (width) x 10cm (depth).
